flowRoot.flowPara: Select a keyboard layout or input method
Initial shortlist shows popular input sources.
Show more expands the list to show all languages.
Search box filters the language list only.
Languages with only one input source can be selected direct from the list. Others show an arrow to navigate to a sub-list.
Alternative keyboard layouts are not included in the list of input sources by default. An option allows them to be shown.
Input method - converts characters typed in one alphabet into another alphabet.
Converts characters typed in one alphabet into another alphabet.
